#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:812,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:812
msgid ""
"Determines what happens when someone visits a default WordPress "
"authentication URL (%s). Only applies when custom pages above have been set. "
"Caution: If hiding default paths, remember your custom page URLs to avoid "
"lockout."
msgstr ""
"Menentukan perkara yang berlaku apabila seseorang melawat URL pengesahan "
"WordPress lalai (%s). Hanya terpakai apabila halaman tersuai di atas telah "
"ditetapkan. Awas: Jika menyembunyikan laluan lalai, ingat URL halaman "
"tersuai anda untuk mengelakkan sekatan."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:816,
#: ../build/bricks/includes/elements/filter-submit.php:52,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:816,
#: ../includes/elements/filter-submit.php:52
msgid "Redirect to"
msgstr "Ubah hala ke"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:827,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:827
msgid ""
"When someone visits a default WordPress authentication URL (%s), they are "
"redirected to this selected page."
msgstr ""
"Apabila seseorang melawat URL pengesahan WordPress lalai (%s), mereka diubah "
"hala ke halaman yang dipilih ini."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:832,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:832
msgid "Disable custom authentication page bypass"
msgstr "Lumpuhkan pintasan halaman pengesahan tersuai"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:835,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:835
msgid ""
"By default, users can access the default WordPress auth pages by adding %1$s "
"to the URL, bypassing custom authentication pages. Enable this setting to "
"remove this bypass option and always use your custom authentication pages "
"and behavior as set above."
msgstr ""
"Secara lalai, pengguna boleh mengakses halaman pengesahan WordPress lalai "
"dengan menambahkan %1$s pada URL, memintas halaman pengesahan tersuai. "
"Dayakan tetapan ini untuk mengalih keluar pilihan pintasan ini dan sentiasa "
"gunakan halaman dan gelagat pengesahan tersuai anda seperti yang ditetapkan "
"di atas."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:848,
#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:856,
#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:897,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:848,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:856,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:897
msgid "User activation"
msgstr "Pengaktifan pengguna"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:849,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:849
msgid ""
"Send an email to every newly registered user with an activation link that "
"must be clicked to activate their account."
msgstr ""
"Hantar e-mel kepada setiap pengguna yang baru berdaftar dengan pautan "
"pengaktifan yang mesti diklik untuk mengaktifkan akaun mereka."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:850,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:850
msgid ""
"There is an \"Activation status\" column under \"Users\", where you can "
"manually set the status to active/inactive and resend the activation email."
msgstr ""
"Terdapat lajur \"Status pengaktifan\" di bawah \"Pengguna\", di mana anda "
"boleh menetapkan status secara manual kepada aktif/tidak aktif dan "
"menghantar semula e-mel pengaktifan."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:857,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:857
msgid ""
"Enable to require user to verify the email after registration through an "
"activation link."
msgstr ""
"Membolehkan pengguna untuk mengesahkan e-mel selepas pendaftaran melalui "
"pautan pengaktifan."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:858,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:858
msgid ""
"This feature affects all new user registrations, not just those submitted "
"via the Form element."
msgstr ""
"Ciri ini mempengaruhi semua pendaftaran pengguna baharu, bukan hanya yang "
"diserahkan melalui elemen Borang."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:863,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:863
msgid "Auto login after activation"
msgstr "Log masuk automatik selepas pengaktifan"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:864,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:864
msgid ""
"Enable to automatically log the user in after successful email verification."
msgstr ""
"Dayakan untuk log masuk pengguna secara automatik selepas pengesahan e-mel "
"berjaya."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:868,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:868
msgid "Verification success page"
msgstr "Halaman kejayaan pengesahan"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:881,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:881
msgid "Verification failure page"
msgstr "Halaman kegagalan pengesahan"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:936,
#: ../build/bricks/includes/elements/form.php:1288,
#: ../build/bricks/includes/elements/form.php:1459,
